                <div class="features-intro clearfix">
                    <h2>Key Skill Areas</h2>

                    <p>The aim of the CDT is to train a world-class cohort of researchers in the theory and practice of a new generation of autonomous intelligent machines and systems. Training will be provided in four interconnected skills areas, the synthesis of which is key to building autonomy in AIMS applications.</p>
                    <a class="read-more" href="http://aims.robots.ox.ac.uk/how-to-apply/">How to Apply</a>                </div>
            </div>
