                            <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-9">
                                <h3>
                                    Robotics, Vision and Perception                                </h3>
                                <p>Enabling autonomous systems to identify and interpret complex scenes, from moving vehicles to human activity and form robust situation assessments to enable appropriate action and decision making.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 single-feature">
